  - Transport, waste, air, safe-street, clinic and vendor-zone outcomes deliver karein
  - Complaints, recusals, recoveries, whistleblower safety and appeals audit karein
  - Targets, misses, costs and corrections ka equal-question public report defend
    karein
  - Independent panel par four outcomes and full-term public audit dekhein
